---
title: Smart Blueberry-Dressed Chicken Breasts Salad with Almond Pralines
description: A summery salad that is this simple and tasty is good any time of the year! Mixed greens are tossed in a stellar blueberry vinaigrette, while roasted chicken brings a filling protein hit. And who can say no to sweet and crunchy almond pralines to top things off?!

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amount.
